  "id": "guide/i18n-common-add-package",
  "title": "Add the localize package",
  "contents": "\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-add-package.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"add-the-localize-package\" translation-result=\"on\">添加本地化包<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#add-the-localize-package\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"add-the-localize-package\">Add the localize package<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#add-the-localize-package\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要利用 Angular 的本地化功能，请用 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 将 <code>@angular/localize</code> 包添加到你的项目中。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To take advantage of the localization features of Angular, use the <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> to add the <code>@angular/localize</code> package to your project.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要添加 <code>@angular/localize</code> 包，请使用如下命令来更新项目中的 <code>package.json</code> 和 <code>polyfills.ts</code> 文件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To add the <code>@angular/localize</code> package, use the following command to update the <code>package.json</code> and <code>polyfills.ts</code> files in your project.</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"i18n/doc-files/commands.sh\" region=\"add-localize\">\nng add @angular/localize\n\n</code-example>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">有关 <code>package.json</code> 和 <code>polyfill</code> 包的更多信息，请参阅<a href=\"guide/npm-packages\" title=\"Workspace npm dependencies | Angular\">工作区的 npm 依赖项</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For more information about <code>package.json</code> and <code>polyfill.ts</code> files, see <a href=\"guide/npm-packages\" title=\"Workspace npm dependencies | Angular\">Workspace npm dependencies</a>.</p>\n\n</div>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果尚未安装 <code>@angular/localize</code>，而你试图构建此项目的本地化版本，<a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 就会报错。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If <code>@angular/localize</code> is not installed and you try to build a localized version of your project, the <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> generates an error.</p>\n\n<!--todo: add example error -->\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" translation-result=\"on\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"whats-next\">What's next<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID | Angular\">通过 ID 引用语音环境</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID | Angular\">Refer to locales by ID</a></p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间： 10/7/2021</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-common-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#add-the-localize-package\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#whats-next\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - guide/npm-packages\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-add-package.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n-->"
}